- Separate the steps of 'r.coverage'
    - initialization and data distribution (5);
    - calculation (3);
    - result gathering (2).
- Implement GPU kernels for each of the steps in the coverage prediction
    - divide input data in radius-sized chunks with offsets (2);
    - path-loss calculation, using an empirical mathematical model
        - line-of-sight calculation (output is a bit matrix) (4);
        - terrain height (2);
        - terrain type (2).
    - apply antenna gain, based on its diagram (2)
    - apply Tx power (1)

